  • Constructor Details

    • DiscordJv

      public DiscordJv(String token, EnumSet<Intent> intents, APIVersion version) throws ExecutionException, InterruptedException
      Creates a new instance of the DiscordJv class This will start the connection to the Discord gateway, set caches, set the event dispatcher, set the logger, set up eliminate handling, and initiates no shutdown
      Parameters:
      token - The token of the bot
      intents - The intents the bot will use
      version - The version of the Discord API the bot will use
      Throws:
      ExecutionException - If an error occurs while connecting to the gateway
      InterruptedException - If an error occurs while connecting to the gateway

    • registerCommands

      public void registerCommands(CommandListener... listeners)
      Registers command(s) with Discord.
      Parameters:
      listeners - The listeners/commands to register
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException -
      • If the command name is less than 1 character or more than 32 characters
      • If the command description is less than 1 character or more than 100 characters
      • If the command options are more than 25
      • If a command option name is less than 1 character or more than 32 characters
      • If a command option description is less than 1 character or more than 100 characters
      • If a command option choices are more than 25
      • If a command option choice name is less than 1 character or more than 100 characters
      • If a command option choice value is less than 1 character or more than 100 characters
